00:00:09.519 --> 00:00:11.669
the President back whenever the

00:00:11.679 --> 00:00:14.310
election was over, the Lord said, 'You

00:00:14.320 --> 00:00:16.550
must pray him through the inauguration,

00:00:16.560 --> 00:00:18.390
for there will be many attacks trying to

00:00:18.400 --> 00:00:21.590
come against him, against his life,

00:00:21.590 --> 00:00:21.600
and

00:00:21.600 --> 00:00:25.870
against the inauguration

00:00:25.870 --> 00:00:25.880
