00:00:25.880 --> 00:00:28.950
said this is going to be a time of

00:00:28.960 --> 00:00:31.589
great intercessory prayer, and that's

00:00:31.599 --> 00:00:33.950
exactly what we set out to do. The Lord

00:00:33.960 --> 00:00:35.350
