00:00:45.160 --> 00:00:47.389
that I'm going to show you as a watchman

00:00:47.399 --> 00:00:50.029
on the wall.'That's exactly what

00:00:50.039 --> 00:00:52.069
we've set out to do on this

00:00:52.069 --> 00:00:52.079
channel—to

00:00:52.079 --> 00:00:54.510
pray to change things. That's what we

00:00:54.520 --> 00:00:56.990
named our church: Prayer Changes

00:00:57.000 --> 00:00:59.549
Things. Prayer Church

00:00:59.559 --> 00:01:01.509
was taken and Prayer Foundation was

00:01:01.519 --> 00:01:03.029
