00:01:04.920 --> 00:01:06.350
that's what they had in the state of

00:01:06.360 --> 00:01:08.789
Oklahoma. We're excited

00:01:08.799 --> 00:01:10.390
to call it Prayer Changes Things because

00:01:10.400 --> 00:01:12.789
that's what we believe here.

00:01:14.799 --> 00:01:17.630
Thank you for joining me in

00:01:17.640 --> 00:01:21.910
praying. I believe our prayers changed a

00:01:21.920 --> 00:01:24.350
lot of things these last

00:01:24.360 --> 00:01:25.870
